{
	"Introduction": "Aloha, young farmer.#$b#You must have followed your nose!$h#$b#I'm Pika. I own Pika's, an outdoor restaurant in the heart of the village.#$b#I'm from Ember Island, in the Fern Islands, where we speak Samaowaii.#$b#Perhaps I'll teach you some!$h",

